# Description
The guild represents those who make things for their looks or artistic merit rather than for usefulness. It is an organization torn by internal strife, and their leader, [[person/Salvatore Celinni|Salvatore Celinni]], is considered an upstart who only became leader due to family connections.

This is one of the five "great guilds" that control much of what happens in Haven and they meet in the [[landmark/Guildhall of the Artisan|Guildhall of the Artisan]]

